snippet.title: Barnaba feat Diamond Platnumz - Salama (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Music video by  Barnaba and Diamond Platnumz tells the emotional story of a man reaching out to his ex-lover, asking how she’s doing now that she’s moved on. The lyrics reveal a mix of reflection and subtle confrontation, as he acknowledges that she seems to be thriving in a new relationship filled with peace, joy, and genuine love—something they lacked in the past. The song carries an undertone of regret and unresolved emotions, while also calling out the ex for once treating him as if he wasn’t good enough. Now, having found someone who truly values him, he indirectly questions her past judgments. It’s a soulful, melodic piece that explores themes of growth, healing, and the bittersweet nature of moving on. This song marks Barnaba’s Celebrations of 16 years in his role as a performing artist while still having a lot to achieve he remains focused to achieve a lot and climb heights of excellency on his music journey, while you listen to this track be inspired of greatness and enjoy the best sounds from the best. The music Video was shot in Dar es Salaam, Directed by Folex.

snippet.title: Diamond Platnumz feat Bien - Katam (Official Lyric Audio)
snippet.description:
Get Katam👇👇👇
https://dplatnumz.lnk.to/katam

"KATAM" is a sweet, catchy love anthem that brings together two East African powerhouses—Diamond Platnumz and @BienOfficial in a celebration of beauty, love, and unity across the continent. The song produced by S2Kizzy is all about that one special woman who leaves you completely speechless—her vibe, her shape, her roots—everything about her is katam tam, meaning irresistibly sweet. Through playful lyrics and smooth harmonies, Diamond and Bien paint a picture of a woman whose charm reflects the richness of East Africa—from her Rwandan glow, Somali hair, Ethiopian eyes, to her Tanzanian sweetness and Kenyan smarts. It's flirty, fun, and full of pride—an Afro-pop jam that makes you want to dance, fall in love, and raise a toast to all the beautiful queens of Africa."

snippet.title: إتقان العصير 🍹🥰 حيلة المناديل للحفاظ على مشروبك آمن!
snippet.description:
🤩✨اغتنموا الفرصة واشتركوا معنا للحصول على جرعة يومية من الإبداع والمرح!
# مبتكرة #اصنع_بنفسك #حرف #تجديد

هذا الفيديو معدّ لأغراض ترفيهية. ولا نقدم أيّ ضمانات بشأن سلامة المحتوى، شموليته أو موثوقيته. أيّ إجراء تقوم به بناءً على المعلومات الواردة في هذا الفيديو هو حصراً مسؤوليتك الخاصة، ولن نكون مسؤولين عن أيّ أضرار أو خسائر. مسؤولية تحرّي الحكمة والحيطة وإجراءات السلامة تقع على عاتق المشاهد إن كان يخطط لتقليد ما يراه في الفيديو.
قد يظهر في الفيديو التالي نشاط تم تنفيذه بواسطة ممثلين ضمن بيئة خاضعة للرقابة - يرجى توخي الحذر إن كنت تخطط لتنفيذه بنفسك.
